==Albanian==

===Etymology 1===
* According to Orel, the particle and conjunction are etymologically identical. From {{inh|sq|sqj-pro|*a}} and cognate to {{cog|grc|ἦ||indeed}}.<ref>{{R:sq:Orel|'''a''' part. ('whether'), conj. ('or')|page=1}}</ref>

* From {{inh|sq|sqj-pro|*(h)au}}, from {{der|sq|ine-pro|*h₂eu-||that}}. Cognate to {{cog|grc|αὖ||on the other hand, again}}. A proclitic disjunctive particle, used with one or more parts of the sentence.

===Alternative forms===
* {{alter|sq|ha}} (''archaic, [[w:Gjon Buzuku|Buzuku]]'')<ref>{{R:sq:Mann:1948|page=1}}</ref>

====Pronunciation====
* {{IPA|sq|/a/}}

====Conjunction====
{{head|sq|conjunctions}}

# [[or]]
# [[there]]

===Etymology 2===
From {{inh|sq|sqj-pro|*(h)an}}, from {{inh|sq|ine-pro|*h₂en||there}}. Cognate with {{cog|la|an||yes, perhaps}}. Interrogative particle, usually used proclitically in simple sentences.

====Pronunciation====
* {{IPA|sq|/a/}}

====Particle====
{{head|sq|particles}}

# [[probably]], [[perhaps]]
# [[whether]]

====Letter====
{{head|sq|letter|lower case||upper case|A}}

# {{n-g|The first letter of the Standard [[Albanian]] Latin-script alphabet.}}

===See also===
{{list:Latin script letters/sq/simple}}
<!--* {{list:Greek script letters/aat}}-->

