===Etymology 8===
From {{der|nb|da|ah||oh}}, likely from {{der|nb|de|ach||oh}}, from {{der|nb|gmh|ach}}, from {{der|nb|goh|ah}}. Also see {{m|nb|ah}} and {{m|nb|akk}}.

