Mostly likely from Norwegian {{m|nb|ad||against, on}}, from {{der|nb|da|ad||by, at}}, from {{der|nb|gmq-oda|at}}, from {{der|nb|non|at||at, to}}, from {{der|nb|gem-pro|*at||at, toward, to}}, from {{der|nb|ine-pro|*h₂éd||to, at}}.

