#: {{uxi|sw|kiini '''cha''' yai|egg yolk|lit=center '''of''' egg}}
#* {{RQ:Abdallah bin Ali Inkishafi|line=9|passage=كِطَّمْسِكِزَ '''گَ'''وُجُهَّالِ ، نُرُ نَمِيَاغَ اِتَظَلَالِ|tr=Kiṭamsi-kiza '''cha'''-ujuhali, nuru na-mianga itaẓalali|translation=Brightness and lights will overcome the shadow and darkness '''of''' ignorance}}

