# [[one]]
#* {{quote-book|yol|year=1867|title=GLOSSARY OF THE DIALECT OF FORTH AND BARGY|passage='''A''' chi of barach.|translation='''A''' little barley.|page=30}}

===Etymology 3===
From {{inh|yol|enm|a}}, unstressed variant of {{m|enm|on}}, {{m|enm|of}}.

====Pronunciation====
* {{IPA|yol|/ə/}}

====Preposition====
{{head|yol|prepositions}}

# [[on]]
